ut for being professional and reliable and safe environment and great for socialization. Pet owners appreciate the attention to detail and the genuine care shown to every furry visitor. For more information, call (513) 931-6139. Visit their website for additional details.\",\"slug\":\"animal-house\",\"address\":\"7869 Hamilton Ave\",\"street\":\"7869 Hamilton Ave\",\"city\":\"Cincinnati\",\"state\":\"OH\",\"zipCode\":\"45231\",\"full_address\":\"7869 Hamilton Ave, Cincinnati, OH 45231, USA\",\"latitude\":39.236847,\"longitude\":-84.54806700000002,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJAa840qBLQIgRCQhsyTU5ZTA\",\"phone\":\"(513) 931-6139\",\"website\":\"http://animalhousecincinnati.com/\",\"rating\":4.3,\"reviewCount\":841,\"userRatingsTotal\":841,\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"unknown\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"10:30 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"10:30 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"10:30 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"10:30 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"10:30 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"10:30 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"11:00 AM – 7:00 PM\"},\"faqs\":[],\"amenities\":{},\"photo\":null,\"photos\":[{\"url\":null,\"type\":\"photo\",\"source\":\"website\"}],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJQcRw1QtLQIgRIa3j06I2XRA\",\"name\":\"Aquatics & Exotics\",\"businessType\":\"Indoor Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Aquatics & Exotics has become a favorite among Cincinnati residents, boasting a 4.4-star rating from 479 satisfied customers. The facility excels in spacious play areas and peace of mind for owners, making it a trusted choice for pet owners who want the best for their pets. For more information, call (513) 521-5500. Visit their website for additional details.\",\"slug\":\"aquatics-exotics\",\"address\":\"7513 Hamilton Ave\",\"street\":\"7513 Hamilton Ave\",\"city\":\"Cincinnati\",\"state\":\"OH\",\"zipCode\":\"45231\",\"full_address\":\"7513 Hamilton 